encyclopedia.cleaver.body=This colossal cleaver isn't just for combat; it's a true warrior's multi-tool.%1%1Not only does it function as the ultimate defense against mobs, but its legendary sharpness allows you to collect mob heads, perfect for crafting and decorating.%1%1§oRequires the Tinkers' Anvil to craft.
encyclopedia.cobalt.body=Tool Head%1%1Durability: 800%1Harvest Tier: Diamond%1Mining Speed: 6.5%1Attack Damage: 2.25%1%1Tool Handle/Guard%1%1Durability: 1.05x%1Mining Speed 1x%1Attack Damage: 1x%1Trait: Killager
encyclopedia.dagger.body=This compact weapon may be shorter than a sword, but it packs a punch in close combat.%1%1While not the strongest, the dagger is a reliable and versatile companion for any adventurer.%1%1§oRequires the Tinkers' Station to craft.
